Package org.soen6441.adapterpattern

Class Adaptee

java.lang.Object
org.soen6441.adapterpattern.Adaptee
public class Adaptee
extends java.lang.Object
This is the Adaptee class which has loadmap and savemap functions for the conquest map type. Adptee's functionality is similar to the target but it is used for another type of map file.

  • Method Details

    • loadConquestMap

      public java.lang.String loadConquestMap​(java.lang.String p_S, GameEngine p_GameEngine)
      This method load another type of map file called the conquest file. After reading from the conquest file, it stores in to the same Map object which is created for the domination file type.
      Parameters:
      p_S - argument which contains the name of the conquest map file
      p_GameEngine - GameEngine object which will internally have Map object in which we will load all the continents, countries and their borders.
      Returns:
      success or error for the implementation of this function

    • saveConquestMap

      public java.lang.String saveConquestMap​(java.lang.String p_S, GameEngine p_GameEngine)
      This method saves another type of map in the file type called the conquest map file. For each continent, country and their respective border stored in the Map object inside GameEngine, it saves them into the file at their respective places.
      Parameters:
      p_S - argument This argument contains name of the file inside we want to save.
      p_GameEngine - GameEngine object which will internally have Map object from which we will save all the continents, countries and their borders.
      Returns:
      success or error for the implementation of this function
